[h3 id=Theproblemsaboutthesoundplugin. 
	" The problems about the sound plugin. 
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Some sounds are lost in TAS Sound Plugin of Move sync mode. 
	$LF
	"MIDAS PSX SPU does not desync, it may be good. 
	$LF
	"But, they may freeze by a  Cortex's voice because reading of the sound is out of condition. 
	$LF
	"It may be necessary you do not use the mode or to change it into other SPU so that you watch the end.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=MovementTricks 
	" Movement Tricks
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=Zigzagboost 
	" Zigzag boost
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Crash's speed is boosted, if you continue pressing D-pad diagonally while sliding or jumping.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=SlideandSpinofneutral 
	" Slide and Spin of neutral
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Sliding speed is kept when Crash spin.
	$LF
	"But, it becomes low speed if you press D-pad when Crash spin.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Abouttheice 
	" About the ice
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"When you jump from ice, slippery ground is carried over to the moment of the next landing, and it is continued if you jump again.
	$LF
	"In addition, you can slide at fast speed only once.
	$LF
]p
