[h3 id=ExtraItemGlitch 
	" Extra Item Glitch
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"When Crash stamped a box, the counts that stamped an enemy consecutively increase in the same way. 
	$LF
	"And you can get a extra item when this counts exceed 200 times.
	$LF
]p
