[h4 id=Keepthecounter 
	" Keep the counter
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"When Crash lands, this counter is initialized, but it is continued if Crash land while spin.
	$LF
	"And it is continued while Crash slide and squat down.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Spinningstamp 
	" Spinning stamp 
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"I was able to cancel the bounce of Crash by spinning at the same time to stamp the bounds limit of the box. 
	$LF
	"And it is applied to an enemy.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Slidingstamp 
	" Sliding stamp 
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"You would stamp it when you jumped as soon as slide attack the enemy.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=Detailedcommentary 
	" Detailed commentary
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"At first 197 times bound. It saves 30 frames about once to hit a head on an object.
	$LF
	"And, I stamped 17 enemies after having stamped three boxes while letting the counter continue.
	$LF
	"I was able to continue the counter to the next scene by stepping on the pedestal with spin.
	$LF
	"However, unfortunately it was not able to continue when a scene was replaced by a fall.
	$LF
	"Therefore I stamped 8 enemies more in second scene.
	$LF
]p
